<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Krypton | Verificação de E-mail</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#0f172a] text-slate-100 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">
  <div class="max-w-md w-full bg-slate-900/60 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-xl space-y-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-black text-violet-400">Verificação de Segurança</h1>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2">Para acessar o painel de administração, valide o seu e-mail corporativo ou pessoal.</p>
    </div>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 p-3 rounded-xl text-xs text-center">
        <%= error %>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <form action="/verify-email" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Endereço de E-mail</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="exemplo@dominio.com" class="w-full bg-slate-950 p-3.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 focus:border-violet-500 text-sm outline-none transition" required />
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-violet-600 hover:bg-violet-500 text-white font-bold py-3.5 rounded-xl transition text-sm shadow-lg shadow-violet-600/20">
        Enviar Código de Segurança
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
